{"tid":640950,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[子華] 論\"原價放售\" Vs \"黃牛飛\"","createTime":"2018-04-24T16:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T01:40:43.000Z","uid":43045,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"31e305525364323587e2e185bc73919f6c9988f9","tid":640950,"uid":43045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:03:56.000Z","msg":"見到在座咁多位巴絲, 互相幫助, 買多左既人願意用原價放售比買唔到既人, 但接下落黎就引伸左下一個問題:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到最後, &quot;黃牛飛&quot; 炒唔起, 佢地最後都係用原價放售, 市場上都有一班人搶住接貨, 變相&quot;黃牛飛&quot;可以說係無本生利, 係一個零風險既生意, 所以之後&quot;黃牛飛&quot;都依舊會出現<br />\n<br />\n敢問各位, 嚮呢個未有實名制管制既環境之下, 可以如果分辨 &quot;原價放售&quot;  同 &quot;黃牛飛&quot;原價放售, 從而懲罰呢班 &quot;黃牛飛&quot; 小人呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 已買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54913a00e213a17aa987babf533aa6e038b9d74","tid":640950,"uid":77788,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:09:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2af3a0cc864a11d1f90bdff344b3abd65690fa8","tid":640950,"uid":43045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a54913a00e213a17aa987babf533aa6e038b9d74","tid":640950,"uid":77788,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:09:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:10:33.000Z","msg":"巴打又幾岩, 真係唔知幫到FANS定幫左炒家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36cd7ec86484ce4a59cc7648f41d567f16b7d94","tid":640950,"uid":55506,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"佢地請蝻排原價放點會唔蝕呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45aa1637bfba6b1beb90d9e579520c8baa2d3faa","tid":640950,"uid":129708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2af3a0cc864a11d1f90bdff344b3abd65690fa8","tid":640950,"u